WEBVTT

00:00:00.884 --> 00:00:06.343
"Where are you from?"
said the pale, tattooed man.

00:00:07.583 --> 00:00:11.103
"Where are you from?"

00:00:12.453 --> 00:00:15.493
It's September 21, 2001,

00:00:16.533 --> 00:00:21.615
10 days after the worst attack
on America since World War II.

00:00:22.715 --> 00:00:26.940
Everyone wonders about the next plane.

00:00:26.940 --> 00:00:29.682
People are looking for scapegoats.